sequenceDiagram
    participant Admin as Cluster Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant DSCICtrl as DSCInitialization<br/>Controller
    participant DSCCtrl as DataScienceCluster<br/>Controller
    participant CompReg as Component Registry
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller<br/>(e.g. KServe)
    participant Manifests as /opt/manifests/<br/>(Filesystem)
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant SMCtrl as ServiceMesh<br/>Controller
    participant MonCtrl as Monitoring<br/>Controller

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
    Note over Admin, DSCICtrl: Flow 1: Platform Initialization
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DSCInitialization CR
    K8sAPI->>DSCICtrl: Watch event (CR created)
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create namespaces<br/>SA token auth
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply NetworkPolicies<br/>SA token auth
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Auth service CR
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Monitoring service CR
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMesh service CR
    DSCICtrl->>K8sAPI: Configure CA bundles
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
    Note over Admin, CompCtrl: Flow 2: Component Deployment
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create DataScienceCluster CR
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch event (CR created)
    DSCCtrl->>CompReg: Iterate registered components
    CompReg-->>DSCCtrl: Component handlers list
    loop For each enabled component
        DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Component CR<br/>(e.g. Kserve, Dashboard)<br/>SA token auth
        K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch event (Component CR)
        CompCtrl->>Manifests: Read kustomize manifests
        Manifests-->>CompCtrl: YAML resources
        CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Server-side apply resources<br/>SA token auth
    end
    K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Status updates
    end

    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
    Note over Admin, Webhook: Flow 3: Webhook Admission
    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resource<br/>(Notebook, InferenceService, etc.)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-* or /validate-*<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: Read HardwareProfiles,<br/>Connections, Kueue config<br/>SA token auth
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit/Deny + mutations<br/>(inject resources, labels, env vars)
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: Response
    end

    rect rgb(237, 231, 246)
    Note over SMCtrl, K8sAPI: Flow 4: Service Mesh Initialization
    K8sAPI->>SMCtrl: ServiceMesh CR watch event
    SMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMeshControlPlane<br/>SA token auth
    SMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Deploy Authorino instance<br/>SA token auth
    SMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Patch SMCP with Authorino<br/>external authz extension
    SMCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create mesh-refs ConfigMap<br/>SA token auth
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
    Note over MonCtrl, K8sAPI: Flow 5: Monitoring Stack Deployment
    K8sAPI->>MonCtrl: Monitoring CR watch event
    MonCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create MonitoringStack (COO)<br/>SA token auth
    MonCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create TempoMonolithic (Tempo)<br/>SA token auth
    MonCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create OpenTelemetryCollector<br/>SA token auth
    MonCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create per-component<br/>PrometheusRules<br/>SA token auth
    end
